&lt;li&gt;Assess employee development needs, make recommendations, and implement appropriate solutions aligned with the organization’s broader strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle complex global employee relations issues, working with leadership to implement best practices and approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
